article_id:1929,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding the Morsayati Reckoning Weekly Bonus,image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed that the number of weekly bonus rewards obtained when clearing the Forgotten Truths: Morsayati Reckoning quest added on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1610604000"></span> is different between the solo and co-op versions of the quest.</div><div><br></div><div>We plan to fix this issue in a data update on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1611554400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>We will also send the difference in number of weekly bonus rewards to all players who have cleared the solo version of this quest before the fix is applied.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1610700600,update_time1610701391